{"tid":1210253,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阮兆祥贊成警察清場：示威破壞某啲香港人生活","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:41:28.000Z","uid":93410,"like":4,"dislike":294,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c81fe41d34c286d24b74686f57796b04fc78d9fc","tid":1210253,"uid":93410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"立法會原定今日《逃犯條例》修例二讀，不少熱心巿民今日響應罷工罷巿罷課，到金鐘政總外示威，最後跟警察發生衝突。有人選擇站出來保護香港的同時，亦可以有不同選擇，實屬無可厚非。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">祥仔阮兆祥就選擇了跟男友人逛街</span></strong>，今日下午5時許，見到祥仔跟友人在商場內找舖頭，最後去了一間連鎖精品店。花了大約20分鐘左右便完成揀禮物及付款離開。他在等電梯時接受《蘋果》訪問，被問到對條例的看法，祥仔說：「有啲支持(內容)有啲反對(內容)。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當然清場係應該嘅，因為始終可能會破壞到某啲香港人生活，我支持佢哋用一個比較溫和理性嘅方式去對待呢件事情</span></strong>，兩面都係我覺得，我期待住一個好嘅成果，我諗無論企喺邊一方，身為香港人都係愛香港，希望香港係好嘅，希望兩面都能夠互相體諒。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190612/large/1560342632_e01f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190612%2Flarge%2F1560342632_e01f.jpg&h=56c83470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（左圖攝影：梁繼光／右圖攝影：董立華）<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0612 20:30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190612/large/1560340280_23ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190612%2Flarge%2F1560340280_23ef.jpg&h=e17c9908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祥仔支持警察清場。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190612/large/1560340280_147e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190612%2Flarge%2F1560340280_147e.jpg&h=48698a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祥仔跟男友人挑選禮物。 （影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n採訪、攝影：梁繼光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新聞有價】6月17日起 繼續撐蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IJ24ZR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IJ24ZR&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=8b560700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IJ24ZR</a> <br />\n--------------------------------<br />\n【記住63836568】全民爆相爆片！下一個爆料王就係你<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Guolu9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Guolu9&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=161351d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Guolu9</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190612/59708444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708444&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=31fb1e91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708444&h=052c3cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190612/59708444</a>"},{"pid":"3154b07fe0087fd2b0637da1b945355450fc3058","tid":1210253,"uid":103237,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"豬"},{"pid":"f3d2a537eaa1aecbacddddacb21f44aca4652628","tid":1210253,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"😅"},{"pid":"bc8d3f8ae0ea42c25073e1140479c1c9c711d95a","tid":1210253,"uid":162095,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"棟篤笑爛gag黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aa7ee456b4f458c0ddf22170f38df2fc98977c","tid":1210253,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeabf23122ca85a0d787b6aeef9f6a6b23cff58","tid":1210253,"uid":167828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac037e1e27f425509f50f01ac7afccd483452fb","tid":1210